This movie has changed my life, the true, raw emotion that this movie presents really shows an amazing example of the human endeavor.
And it's all thanks to that little emoji.
Well I mean, what great sin did I do to have this hellish punishment placed upon me? Maybe it's that I own a device with emojis, and am not currently dead.

"The Emoji Movie (2017)" is a real treat for the whole family.  I am not surprised by the ratings of "The Emoji Movie (2017)" , because only a certain kind of a person (a cultivated and sophisticated person, dare I say so) can actually comprehend the things said and done in the said movie, "The Emoji Movie (2017).  Simply just stunning masterpiece, "The Emoji Movie (2017)" that is.
This is the best movie of all time. I want to touch Jailbreak's vagoober.

So my older cousins and I saw the Emoji Movie around 2 hours ago and oh my GOD. First, the amount of adult jokes. One of my older cousins actually COUNTED how many jokes. How many? 16. And the Only laughs i heard from children was at the short films before the movie started. Overall, it was MEH. 



Plus all the poop jokes were a stupid amount.

People have given this film harsh criticism ever since it was announced, but this is truly the film of the century, incapsulating everything a movie requires to show its excellence. Whether it's the clever jokes and puns strewn about the sub 2 hour film, or the amazing character development we see along Gene's journey, this film will surely impress people of any age. Even your out of touch grandad will surely laugh at jokes like "throw myself on the barbie'"-shrimp emoji??. This groundbreaking film has shown us its humble beginnings and, I predict, that it will will rise to be one of the greatest movie franchises of our generation.??????????????????????????????????????????????????????
